title: TV | At Home with Steph and Dom
text: Gogglebox fans will know couple Steph and Dom well, the posh couple who enjoy a drink or two while watching their favourite programmes... that we in turn then watch them watch. Yeah, Gogglebox is strange when you over-think it, or think about it at all really. Anyways, Steph and Dom have proven so popular with viewers that they have landed their own chat show of sorts. It will see them host a series of celebrity dinners at their plush B&B, with celebrity guests including the likes of Jerry Springer, Jason Donovan, Louis Walsh and Phil Tufnell. It's a one-off show for now but no doubt there will be more where this came from.
